                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "Sentence",
                              "attr": {
                                "Num": "1",
                                "WritingMode": "vertical"
                              },
                              "children": [
                                "この法律は、最近における政治資金をめぐる状況に鑑み、政治に対する国民の信頼の回復を図るため、政治資金監視委員会等の設置その他の政治資金の透明性を確保するための措置等について定めるものとする。"
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tag": "Chapter",
              "attr": {
                "Num": "2"
              },
              "children": [
                {
                  "tag": "ChapterTitle",
                  "attr": {},
                  "children": [
                    "第二章　政治資金監視委員会等の設置"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "tag": "Section",
                  "attr": {
                    "Num": "1"
                  },
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "tag": "SectionTitle",
                      "attr": {},
                      "children": [
                        "第一節　政治資金監視委員会の設置"
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "2"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（設置）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第二条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "政治資金の透明性を確保するため、別に法律で定めるところにより、国会に、政治資金監視委員会（以下「委員会」という。）を置くものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "3"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（組織）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第三条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員会は、委員長及び委員をもって組織するものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "4"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（委員長及び委員の任命）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第四条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員長及び委員は、委員会の職務の遂行に関し公正な判断をすることができ、広い経験と知識を有する者のうちから、両院合同協議会（第十一条に規定する両院合同協議会をいう。第十条において同じ。）の推薦に基づき、両議院の議長が、両議院の承認を得て、これを任命するものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "5"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（委員長及び委員の身分保障）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第五条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員長及び委員は、心身の故障のため職務の遂行ができないこと又は職務の執行上の義務違反その他委員長若しくは委員たるに適しない非行があったことについて両議院の議決があったときを除いては、罷免されることはないものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "6"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（委員長及び委員の服務）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第六条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員長及び委員は、職務上知ることのできた秘密を漏らしてはならないものとする。"
                                  ]
                                },
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "2",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "その職を退いた後も同様とするものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "2"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                "２"
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員長及び委員は、不偏不党かつ公平中正にその職務を行わなければならないものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "3"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                "３"
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員長及び委員は、在任中、政党その他の政治団体の役員となり、又は積極的に政治活動をしてはならないものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "4"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                "４"
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員長及び委員は、他の官職を兼ね、又は公選による公職の候補者となり、若しくは公選による公職と兼ねてはならないものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "7"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（事務局）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第七条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
                            },
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphSentence",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "tag": "Sentence",
                                  "attr": {
                                    "Num": "1",
                                    "WritingMode": "vertical"
                                  },
                                  "children": [
                                    "委員会の事務を処理させるため、委員会に事務局を置くものとする。"
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "tag": "Article",
                      "attr": {
                        "Num": "8"
                      },
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleCaption",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "（監視等）"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "ArticleTitle",
                          "attr": {},
                          "children": [
                            "第八条"
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "tag": "Paragraph",
                          "attr": {
                            "Num": "1"
                          },
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "tag": "ParagraphNum",
                              "attr": {},
                              "children": []
